  "text": "A Svanodip FMDV-Ag kit (Boehringer Ingelheim Svanova, Uppsala, Sweden) was used following the manufacturer's instructions. A total of 170 μl of samples diluted with sample buffer were added to the device and, after 10 min, mABS was measured using the ImmunochromatoReader C10066. [CITATION_1] were used for comparative studies.",
